 begin="3:23.440" end="3:23.630">で</span><span begin="3:23.630" end="3:23.820">も</span><span begin="3:23.820" end="3:24.080">知</span><span begin="3:24.080" end="3:24.280">ら</span><span begin="3:24.280" end="3:24.540">な</span><span begin="3:24.540" end="3:24.710">い</span><span begin="3:24.710" end="3:24.920">ま</span><span begin="3:24.920" end="3:25.150">ま</span><span begin="3:25.150" end="3:25.310">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们至今仍未知晓</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Bokura wa ima demo shiranai mama da</span></p><p begin="3:25.560" end="3:26.180" itunes:key="L53" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:25.560" end="3:25.660">だ</span><span begin="3:25.760" end="3:26.020">け</span><span begin="3:26.020" end="3:26.180">ど</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但是</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dakedo</span></p><p begin="3:26.440" end="3:28.730" itunes:key="L54" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:26.440" end="3:26.860">僕</span><span begin="3:26.860" end="3:27.040">ら</span><span begin="3:27.280" end="3:27.500">に</span><span begin="3:27.500" end="3:27.730">は</span><span begin="3:27.730" end="3:28.170">歌</span><span begin="3:28.170" end="3:28.380">が</span><span begin="3:28.380" end="3:28.590">あ</span><span begin="3:28.590" end="3:28.730">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们拥有歌</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Bokura ni wa uta ga aru</span></p><p begin="3:29.010" end="3:32.180" itunes:key="L55" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:29.010" end="3:29.420">僕</span><span begin="3:29.420" end="3:29.620">ら</span><span begin="3:29.870" end="3:30.080">に</span><span begin="3:30.080" end="3:30.290">は</span><span begin="3:30.290" end="3:30.720">愛</span><span begin="3:30.720" end="3:30.940">が</span><span begin="3:30.940" end="3:31.500">残</span><span begin="3:31.500" end="3:31.580">っ</span><span begin="3:31.580" end="3:31.770">て</span><span begin="3:31.770" end="3:32.010">い</span><span begin="3:32.010" end="3:32.180">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们还有爱残留</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Bokura ni wa ai ga nokotteiru</span></p><p begin="3:32.430" end="3:35.570" itunes:key="L56" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:32.430" end="3:32.880">答</span><span begin="3:32.880" end="3:33.050">え</span><span begin="3:33.300" end="3:33.470">を</span><span begin="3:33.470" end="3:33.920">探</span><span begin="3:33.920" end="3:34.130">す</span><span begin="3:34.130" end="3:34.360">た</span><span begin="3:34.360" end="3:34.520">め</span><span begin="3:34.520" end="3:35.000">歌</span><span begin="3:35.000" end="3:35.200">う</span><span begin="3:35.200" end="3:35.430">の</span><span begin="3:35.430" end="3:35.570">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">为了寻找答案而歌唱</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kotae o sagasu tame utau no da</span></p><p begin="3:35.850" end="3:38.300" itunes:key="L57" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:35.850" end="3:36.290">僕</span><span begin="3:36.290" end="3:36.470">ら</span><span begin="3:36.470" end="3:36.720">は</span><span begin="3:36.720" end="3:37.150">今</span><span begin="3:37.150" end="3:37.350">で</span><span begin="3:37.350" end="3:37.570">も</span><span begin="3:37.570" end="3:37.780">負</span><span begin="3:37.780" end="3:37.990">け</span><span begin="3:37.990" end="3:38.230">な</span><span begin="3:38.230" end="3:38.300">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们至今仍未认输</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Bokura wa ima demo makenai</span></p><p begin="3:38.600" end="3:41.640" itunes:key="L58" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:38.600" end="3:38.920">そ</span><span begin="3:38.920" end="3:39.480">う</span><span begin="3:39.480" end="3:39.920">だ</span><span begin="3:39.920" end="3:41.610">ろう</span><span begin="3:41.610" end="3:41.640">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是这样吧？</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sou darou?</span></p><p begin="3:42.010" end="3:45.070" itunes:key="L59" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:42.010" end="3:42.340">そ</span><span begin="3:42.340" end=